"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"### 测试开始于将 PolkaIDO 推广到一小组 beta 测试人员\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/vQC22j92pu17WcjwiE4qo.png?height=811&width=1400)\\n\\n早在 6 月份，我们就开始接受 [Polkadex](https://polkadex.trade/) 测试版测试程序的申请。我们收到了来自经验丰富的交易员、早期 Polkadexers 和熟练的开发人员的数百份申请。今天，经过数月对 Polkadex 的几个组件（包括 PolkaIDO、Polkadex Orderbook 和 Polkapool）的工作以及主网成功启动后，Polkadex beta 测试程序终于开始了。\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/polkadex/status/1407304983683420160/photo/1?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1407304983683420160%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.embedly.com%2Fwidgets%2Fmedia.html%3Ftype%3Dtext2Fhtmlkey%3Da19fcc184b9711e1b4764040d3dc5c07schema%3Dtwitterurl%3Dhttps3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpolkadex%2Fstatus%2F1407304983683420160image%3Dhttps3A%2F%2Fi.embed.ly%2F1%2Fimage3Furl3Dhttps253A252F252Fabs.twimg.com252Ferrors252Flogo46x38.png26key3Da19fcc184b9711e1b4764040d3dc5c07](https://twitter.com/polkadex/status/1407304983683420160/photo/1?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1407304983683420160%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.embedly.com%2Fwidgets%2Fmedia.html%3Ftype%3Dtext2Fhtmlkey%3Da19fcc184b9711e1b4764040d3dc5c07schema%3Dtwitterurl%3Dhttps3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpolkadex%2Fstatus%2F1407304983683420160image%3Dhttps3A%2F%2Fi.embed.ly%2F1%2Fimage3Furl3Dhttps253A252F252Fabs.twimg.com252Ferrors252Flogo46x38.png26key3Da19fcc184b9711e1b4764040d3dc5c07)\\n\\n                                           2021 年 6 月的 Beta 测试程序公告\\n\\n## 谁是 Beta 测试人员？\\n\\n我们精心挑选并接触了几十名测试人员，这些测试人员由经验丰富的开发人员、CEX 交易员、DeFi 专业者和新手组成。我们在他们和我们的开发团队之间建立了直接沟通渠道，这将确保解决和修复测试人员可能遇到的任何反馈、问题或问题，并改善整体用户体验\\n\\n## 第一个测试：PolkaIDO\\n\\nPolkadex 测试版测试人员的第一个任务是熟悉 PolkaIDO，发现错误并将其报告给团队。如果您不知道，PolkaIDO 将成为 IDO（初始 Dex 产品）的游戏规则改变者，作为一个更公平、更便宜、更透明的链上 IDO 平台和所有代币生成活动的一站式商店。有关 PolkaIDO 如何改变 IDO 游戏的更多详细信息，请查看下面的文章。 成功解决 beta 测试人员发现的所有错误后，PolkaIDO 将发布到公共测试网。随后 PolkaIDO 自己的主网将在 2021 年第四季度的某个时候发布。\\n\\n## Coming up\\n\\nOther components and updates will follow a similar path of beta testing followed by Testnet releases and finally releasing on Mainnet. After PolkaIDO, Polkadex Orderbook will be thoroughly tested by beta testers in different phases rolled out in different versions. Each version will be released as a new update for beta testers and afterwards rolled out to the public Testnet. Each update will have more and more functionality. After the beta testing of Polkadex Orderbook starts, the final component of the 3 initial components that currently make up the Polkadex vision, Polkapool, will be launched to beta testers.\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/polkaido-launchpad-overview-728bd40effd6](https://medium.com/polkadex/polkaido-launchpad-overview-728bd40effd6)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\n[https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88](https://medium.com/polkadex/understanding-polkadex-polkadex-101-97f8957bae88)\\n\\nAny future products and updates will be tested through the beta tester program before following a similar launch schedule.\\n\\n## The importance of beta testing\\n\\nThe importance of the beta tester program cannot be understated. A constant feedback loop between the Polkadex devs and the beta testers in the final stages of development is crucial for the Polkadex vision to come to life. Beta testers will be incentivized to maintain a high level of quality testing with a generous rewards program. In addition, this marks the first overall release of a component that is part of the Polkadex vision. While many components are yet to be released to beta testers, then the Testnet, and finally, the Mainnet, this is a significant step in the Polkadex release schedule. All in all, the purpose of the beta tester program will be to create a cycle of rigorous testing, open communication, and prompt reiteration that will allow us to make the best version of Polkadex, together.\\n\\n> *While we can’t wait to launch all the different components of Polkadex to the Polkadex Mainnet, we’re super excited to work together with beta testers to make Polkadex the best it can be. Follow the journey in the official Polkadex accounts below!*\\n\\n*[Website](https://www.polkadex.trade/)| [Twitter](https://twitter.com/polkadex) | [TG Chat](https://t.me/Polkadex) | [TG Announcements](https://t.me/PolkadexAnnouncements) | [Medium](https://polkadex.medium.com/) | [Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6fXRDT4lLKlXG3gP0PP06Q) | [Reddit](https://www.reddit.com/r/polkadex/) | [Discord](https://discord.com/invite/Uvua83QAzk) | [Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/company/69690544/admin/) | [Spanish community](https://t.me/Polkadex_Spanish) | [Turkish community](https://t.me/Polkadex_Turkish) | [Indian community](https://t.me/polkadexindia) | [Russian community](https://t.me/PolkadexRussian) | [Chinese community](https://t.me/PolkadexCN) |*\",\"timestamp\":1635244541,\"title\":\"Polkadex Beta-Tester 计划已启动\"},\"digest\":\"UT7Jr-KOnUbgjGfbb1ZQd9jX_9WPM8IjR87rivTbrSY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x005c0d08AF6B0C4b486916A7bd1F64b6fBaBB